{"tid":879536,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"腳膠請進！麻油雞食材正妹用腳踏洗","createTime":"2018-10-28T04:53:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-28T05:02:55.000Z","uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"efb2604a9ef4f4468dd4289576cd59db78876024","tid":879536,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T04:53:23.000Z","msg":"對於這段影片，《蘋果》打電話向該店家求證，接電話的女店員向記者坦承，當時確實是在清洗生薑，因為有時候送來的生薑表皮上有太多泥土，所以才會用腳踩，如此才能讓表皮上的泥土清洗得較乾淨，否則平常都是用手清洗，而且用腳洗的時候，店員都會穿著乾淨的雨鞋。<br />\n不過對照店家的說法，以及民眾所拍下的畫面，畫面中的女店員腳上穿的只是一般拖鞋，並非店家所說的雨鞋，也有網友看完影片留言回應：「怎麼沒脫掉？」另外也有網友補充，確實會有這樣的洗薑方式，洗完後還要將生薑放進滾筒機中去皮，但不清楚該店家的後續處理方式。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20181028/1455591\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20181028%2F1455591&d=IT0WKWL4evWOYlI9S0Ou9AIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=ef66276b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20181028%2F1455591&h=534c8b94\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20181028/1455591</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181028/640_ed6be63b17f1db8b17d16ded06ee0918.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181028%2F640_ed6be63b17f1db8b17d16ded06ee0918.jpg&h=440d32ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a02162ca6e60dc12273df1944a2d6b67319f8d1","tid":879536,"uid":143288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T04:55:17.000Z","msg":"想食埋佢對鞋啲老泥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea7ecaa17d729a81fac769702121167ae2348a6e","tid":879536,"uid":199590,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T04